{"tid":38593,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解一定要大驚先可以報警？","createTime":"2016-12-14T04:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T05:50:23.000Z","uid":17616,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"049764b6ffae304020bf0c63468b33b278c6b923","tid":38593,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:32:51.000Z","msg":"店舖大門捲閘遭塗鴉　保安大驚報警處理 (10:51)<br />\n2015/12/31<br />\n<br />\n17歲中學生將自己反鎖廁所內 校方大驚報警<br />\n 2016-03-15 20:51:25<br />\n<br />\n情困女圖跳橋自殺　男友大驚報警<br />\n07月04日(一) 12:41更新 04:25建立   <br />\n<br />\n誤傳企圖自殺 友人大驚報警 (13:34)<br />\n2015/11/27<br />\n<br />\n香港唐樓梯間現4條蜥蜴 住客大驚報警<br />\n2014年10月27日 14:44    稿件來源：香港《明報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冷靜報警唔得？小小驚報警唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解啲報紙佬知道班人報警個陣一定係大驚？<br />\n定係佢地有份聽999個報案電話，聽到對面喊晒口講野一舊舊咁就知道佢地係大驚緊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無爸絲做報紙可以解答下我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4756549cc1f7f699fbdac29d620da8fb670519ce","tid":38593,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a071bc8b3d27df51bdffcce760036563de5faadc","tid":38593,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e417d8d82d997152ab001e1f0c75b3235b8dcc6","tid":38593,"uid":44933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8dbfaae29f9ed164c6c85a0015c4f129f50c5f","tid":38593,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"呀！！！！！！！係咪999呀！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670c5bc572d8dba10afcaa3a4e34d099542d67e2","tid":38593,"uid":22714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>店舖大門捲閘遭塗鴉　保安大驚報警處理 (10:51)<br />\n2015/12/31<br />\n<br />\n17歲中學生將自己反鎖廁所內 校方大驚報警<br />\n 2016-03-15 20:51:25<br />\n<br />\n情困女圖跳橋自殺　男友大驚報警<br />\n07月04日(一) 12:41更新 04:25建立   <br />\n<br />\n誤傳企圖自殺 友人大驚報警 (13:34)<br />\n2015/11/27<br />\n<br />\n香港唐樓梯間現4條蜥蜴 住客大驚報警<br />\n2014年10月27日 14:44    稿件來源：香港《明報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冷靜報警唔得？小小驚報警唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解啲報紙佬知道班人報警個陣一定係大驚？<br />\n定係佢地有份聽999個報案電話，聽到對面喊晒口講野一舊舊咁就知道佢地係大驚緊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無爸絲做報紙可以解答下我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n順口少少 試下改<br />\n誤傳企圖自殺  友人虎驅一震報警<br />\n<br />\n點睇"},{"pid":"f28e5c666995e27c7344431cd6b169efb7b4d936","tid":38593,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀！！！！！！！係咪999呀！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我！！我！！我、我！見到！！<br />\n道道道道道道道.....閘！俾人....<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">噴左漆啊啊啊!!!!!!!!</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嗚啊啊啊!!!!!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cb9e139993b15f3f7a7d6a15e78cd5075f6e4e","tid":38593,"uid":7969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"大驚係一個人⋯"},{"pid":"9ad2a5d5153d5a548f3f9007d15add3b75720aef","tid":38593,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"5.  斬豬肉聲嚇親細膽師奶報警<br />\n<br />\n一名膽小婦人，下午 2時 20分，到沙田隆亨街市買，當她走到肉檔對開時，疑被肉檔職員手起刀落的斬豬肉聲嚇倒，婦人嚇破膽，受驚之下致電報警，事後由救護車送院治理。<br />\n一名膽小婦人，到沙田隆亨街市買時，報稱被肉檔斬豬肉聲音嚇倒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/124740_3e2cdb164a02c6ec3fe7cf181695c8be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F124740_3e2cdb164a02c6ec3fe7cf181695c8be.jpg&h=cf5c66a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e94ee30cb72fd607fc61d243c51f535ad04822","tid":38593,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5.  斬豬肉聲嚇親細膽師奶報警<br />\n<br />\n一名膽小婦人，下午 2時 20分，到沙田隆亨街市買，當她走到肉檔對開時，疑被肉檔職員手起刀落的斬豬肉聲嚇倒，婦人嚇破膽，受驚之下致電報警，事後由救護車送院治理。<br />\n一名膽小婦人，到沙田隆亨街市買時，報稱被肉檔斬豬肉聲音嚇倒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/124740_3e2cdb164a02c6ec3fe7cf181695c8be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F124740_3e2cdb164a02c6ec3fe7cf181695c8be.jpg&h=cf5c66a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實呢個c9幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125955da6e52dcdd4c498612b286c79c1d7e5f51","tid":38593,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5.  斬豬肉聲嚇親細膽師